---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | InnovativeDynamix">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
		<section class="mb-16">
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">The <span class="electric-text">Engine</span> of Innovation</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 font-medium">Fluidity Marine is the high-tech R&D laboratory within the InnovativeDynamix portfolio, dedicated to redefining the maritime paradigm.</p>
		</section>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-20">
			<div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Fluidity Marine</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Our intellectual property core. This is where the **ABLTV** thrust vectoring system was born through rigorous fluid dynamic simulation and rapid prototyping.</p>
				<a href="/technology" class="text-cyan-400 font-bold hover:underline">View IP Specs &rarr;</a>
			</div>
			
			<div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">InnovativeDynamix</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">The venture vehicle. Managing the transition from laboratory break-throughs to scalable global oceanic infrastructure and aspirational lifestyle anchors.</p>
				<a href="/investors" class="text-cyan-400 font-bold hover:underline">Venture Roadmap &rarr;</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="border-t border-white/5 pt-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">Our Strategic Mission</h2>
			<div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-slate-400">
				<p>We are replacing the 'Appendage Era' of maritime propulsion. By removing mechanical rudders and traditional outboards, we aren't just making boats better—we're making them **digital**.</p>
				<p>Our focus on modularity, 3D-printing, and fluid intelligence allows us to scale production across continents while maintaining the precision of a local laboratory.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
